{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe07aff368","title":"对张云逸来信的复信和批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f5dabd84d1","index":0,"year":1955,"month":9,"day":10,"articleId":"fe07aff368"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji35","name":"毛泽东全集第35卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/35-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji35":{"comments":[{"id":"2981af716b","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张云逸，新中国成立后任中共中央华南分局第二书记、中共广西省委书记、中南军政委员会副主席、全国人大常委会委员，这时因病休养。"},{"id":"5400e790ee","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指张云逸1955年8月14日给毛泽东的信。信中说：我因病休养将有5年了，在这长期过程中，深赖主席及诸同志的关怀和照顾，现在我的身体基本上已恢复。3月间来京参加党的全国代表会议，给我的教育极大；近又参加全国人大一届二次会议，会议通过了第一个五年计划，愈加兴奋。久病之后，加上年龄的关系，体力脑力虽不如普，但应将现有的力量为党为人民的伟大事业奋斗到底，以遂初志，而尽己责。现据医生的意见及我的身体情况，可以一面休养，一面参加一定时间的劳动，较为适宜。我每天除做体力运动外，还能学习党的文件，有时亦参加党的会议和全国人大常委会的会议等。这样，我觉得对身体和精神上都有益处，对工作亦可尽到一点责任。如主席有空时间，令我亲赴轮示亦得将我的情况面陈，尤为至盼。"}],"contents":[{"id":"fb06a54a64","type":"title","text":"对张云逸\"来信的复信和批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"2981af716b","type":"paragraph","text":"云逸同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"5400e790ee","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十四日的信收到。身体有起色，甚感。我同意你的办法，即以休养为主，视身体情况许可，的量看些文件，参加一些觉的和国家机关的会议。为准备六中全会，这些天没有时间，候稍闲时再药谈。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"f18fe933b8","type":"paragraph","text":"祝康吉","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"2e56ab2379","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"78f796d5e0","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五五年九月十日尚昆：","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"a217cab562","type":"paragraph","text":"复张信请转致。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"0525c64837","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"d3a7013975","type":"paragraph","text":"九月十日","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"b136952e2f","type":"paragraph","text":"Q","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"d851687798","type":"paragraph","text":"店","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"d4e7bb89fa","type":"subtitle","text":"三化","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"},{"id":"8db6780566","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东致张云逸信的手稿。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368"}],"page":{"id":"01ce96780c","publicationId":"maoquanji35","articleId":"fe07aff368","start":361,"end":362}}}},"__N_SSG":true}